            "Restrict the cluster security group to trusted internal CIDRs/SGs on port 5439: aws ec2 revoke-security-group-ingress --group-id <SG_ID> --protocol tcp --port 5439 --cidr 0.0.0.0/0",
            "Access the warehouse from within the VPC, or via VPN/PrivateLink, rather than the public internet",
            "Verify: aws redshift describe-clusters --cluster-identifier <CLUSTER> --query \"Clusters[0].PubliclyAccessible\" returns false",
            "Prevent recurrence: enable AWS Config rule redshift-cluster-public-access-check org-wide",
