            "Enable audit logging to an S3 bucket (the bucket policy must grant the Redshift log-delivery principal PutObject): aws redshift enable-logging --cluster-identifier <CLUSTER> --bucket-name <LOG_BUCKET>",
            "Alternatively deliver logs to CloudWatch Logs: aws redshift enable-logging --cluster-identifier <CLUSTER> --log-destination-type cloudwatch --log-exports connectionlog userlog useractivitylog",
            "Verify: aws redshift describe-logging-status --cluster-identifier <CLUSTER> shows LoggingEnabled=true",
