            "Ensure an S3 VPC endpoint (and endpoints for any other services the cluster reaches) exists in the cluster's VPC route tables, otherwise COPY/UNLOAD will fail once traffic is forced through the VPC",
            "Enable enhanced VPC routing: aws redshift modify-cluster --cluster-identifier <CLUSTER> --enhanced-vpc-routing",
            "Add VPC endpoint policies and SG egress rules to constrain which S3 buckets the cluster may reach",
            "Verify EnhancedVpcRouting=true via describe-clusters and test a COPY/UNLOAD job",
            "Prevent recurrence: enable AWS Config rule redshift-enhanced-vpc-routing-enabled org-wide",
